<plot>Losing Will is a film about friendship. After suffering paralysis due to a car accident caused by his best friend Jerry, Will decides that he wants to end his own life. He informs his friends that he wants to go on a road trip to the town that he grew up in. Driving through rural Canada in a beat-up RV with their mutual friend Samuels, Jerry struggles with the burden he still carries while Will wonders whether death is actually worth it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?343435</url></doc>
